input.command:
creao-builder-cli database_generate_schema << 'EOF'
{
  "description": "Update the time_card_entry table to include lunch break tracking. The table records work shift entries with clock-in and clock-out times, and system fields (id, data_creator, data_updater, create_time, update_time). Add three optional fields: lunch_start_timestamp (string) - when employee started lunch break, lunch_end_timestamp (string) - when employee ended lunch break, and lunch_duration_minutes (number) - total lunch break duration in minutes. The table also has user_id (foreign key to user table), clock_in_timestamp (string), clock_out_timestamp (string, nullable), total_hours (number, nullable), notes (string, nullable), location (string, nullable), and work_description (string, nullable)."
}
EOF

